Terrorsaur:





Terrorsaur stopped, taking a moment to check his scanners. Rowdy Wolf nearly 
bumped into his back-side. He turned a glance at him, then went back to his 
scanners. He frowned, trying to figure them out.

I...I don't know where he is." he said. "My scanner's are going hay-wire." 
He shook his head. "But, I think we're near-by." He said to Drill-bit: "Just 
keep going, we should hit an entrance."
